  <name>Binary</name>
  <summary>Number base converter</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>A small and simple app used to convert between different number bases. Currently supports conversions between binary and decimal, with planned support for hexadecimal and octal numbers.</p>
	</description>
  <screenshots>
    <screenshot type="default">
